= Vert.x Apex

The link:apidocs/io/vertx/ext/apex/core/Router.html[`router`] is really cool stuff, here is an example

[source,{lang}]
----
Router router = Router.router(vertx);
Router subRouter = Router.router(vertx);

router.mountSubRouter("/subpath", subRouter);

subRouter.route("/foo").handler(rc -> {
  rc.response().setStatusMessage(rc.request().path()).end();
});
----